@API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5062
@ApiKey = STEM-PT-DEV-KEY-2026

### Devices — list
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Device — detail with boards (replace {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices/1
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Boards of a device (replace {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices/1/boards
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dictionaries — list
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Standard dictionary (standalone)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries/standard
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dictionary — detail (replace {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries/1
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Dictionary — resolved variables (standard + device-specific, replace {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/dictionaries/2/resolved
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Commands — list
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/commands
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Commands enabled for a device (replace {deviceId})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/commands/device/1
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Board definition — Production.Tracker format (replace {id})
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/boards/1/definition
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Test without API Key — must return 401
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/devices
Accept: application/json

### Health check — no auth, must return 200 Healthy
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/health

### Version — no auth, returns version and environment
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/version
Accept: application/json
